a6a713fce12e18b1e27795b6ed63ce5b","tid":562954,"uid":90577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f475807e402388e61bfb5cf377a97e6ac37fa696","tid":562954,"uid":164496,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T12:27:16.000Z","msg":"一句講哂 睇feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T12:32:58.000Z","msg":"咁即係解釋唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d623ead136875580b376765128b19988adbe9a79","tid":562954,"uid":8243,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T12:38:00.000Z","msg":"鍾意佢有好多興趣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n每次聽佢不停分享就覺得好開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ca50daa917afd084ac6aefedcf42420589069ea","tid":562954,"uid":127519,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T12:38:23.000Z","msg":"專一、有禮貌、有上進心、有理想同時肯實行，唔係得個講字。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最緊要係默契，一個眼神就知對方想講乜，好夾相處好舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b16f41f3226123cd2725fda3737fcb5a8c9dcff","tid":562954,"uid":90577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T12:43:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>專一、有禮貌、有上進心、<span style=\"color: red;\">有理想同時肯實行</span>，唔係得個講字。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最緊要係默契，一個眼神就知對方想講乜，好夾相處好舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁唔怪之得我到今日都係A0<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e098ebafb32b51cdd7d721b48797117ce8f393a","tid":562954,"uid":170062,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T12:56:40.000Z","msg":"男朋友話覺得我容易溝通 <br />\n同安心講心事我知<br />\n<br />\n我就覺得佢好包容我<br />\n講出黎既問題佢唔會聽完就算<br />\n真係會去改去配合我<br />\n另外佢既興趣就係打波同打機<br />\n好少周圍去玩 <br />\n所以我可以好放心佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過我覺得feel真係好重要<br />\n真係鐘意一個人就缺點都變優點<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24b1c4406cc570caa11a308ddcbf304d12fae30d","tid":562954,"uid":28595,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T13:09:33.000Z","msg":"佢細心 聽我話 尊重我 會聽意見<br />\n同佢一齊好幸福<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e54bfb5541b36281a81c8305bb1835692643a60","tid":562954,"uid":90577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T15:03:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12dc2daaea92a45c55a269cc2eb2f6929fd61eec","tid":562954,"uid":77956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T15:05:53.000Z","msg":"相處既時候真係好舒服<br />\n就算乜都唔做齋坐，都唔會尷尬"},{"pid":"a0e8b4d371ada4482b42a2f08a43a417e2539fd3","tid":562954,"uid":20696,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T17:01:27.000Z","msg":"專一，對感情認真，老實唔講大話唔貪心，價值觀好正確，正直、有原則但唔迂腐，有所為有所不為。脾氣好，會氹我唔嫌我煩唔會發我脾氣，識體諒人又識反省自己。佢唔完美但從來唔會為自己身上不足嘅地方而自卑，無乜負能量，相處好輕鬆。令我有種可以安心依靠嘅感覺，有有時候好似細路仔咁嗲下我好可愛。愛我又對我好，感情台見到嘅感情問題幾乎唔存在喺我地之間，因為佢太好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外鍾意佢俾到我嘅安全感，同佢一齊唔需要懷疑佢愛唔愛我幾愛我愛我幾耐會唔會覺得我唔夠好佢會唔會有日唔要我etc，可以由唔相信感情唔相信一生一世唔相信人性去到願意相信佢。我間唔中就會想自閉想避世，覺得全世界都好煩，唯獨是佢令我覺得，見到佢就好開心好安心，見到佢就有動力面對生活<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7304a7297b5c0576e3a5d2a6e53560c3388f8b16","tid":562954,"uid":36163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T19:23:32.000Z","msg":"旁人眼中可能佢有千百樣缺點<br />\n但只要佢有一個&rdquo;你覺得&rdquo;係優點嘅特質 <br />\n你都可以對佢死心塌地<br />\n<br />\n我諗我鍾意我男朋友簡單直接<br />\n就算佢做衰嘢 只要用直線思考模式去諗<br />\n其實都已經估到佢想點 有時懷疑佢腦得56k<br />\n唔使估估下嘅感覺真係好爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd4ab3a2d5d5eba6e5127eab7b2052b304414c91","tid":562954,"uid":16846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T21:27:56.000Z","msg":"佢救番我條命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01e9bb42b7adb79d5a7fc48c53eff33ff185d087","tid":562954,"uid":90577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fd4ab3a2d5d5eba6e5127eab7b2052b304414c91","tid":562954,"uid":16846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T21:27:56.000Z","msg":"佢救番我條命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T02:04:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\ndetail please<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67dd726b3e867a4d6bbafbd920b479345ac6e5ca","tid":562954,"uid":149357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T04:37:39.000Z","msg":"相處舒服<br />\n比到安全感我<br />\n總之令我想一直同佢一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f97b75fd4416f0b6e871fc919a7a6fe1a9b7b083","tid":562954,"uid":64145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T04:43:24.000Z","msg":"睇黎大部分絲打都中意蠢蠢地嘅人<br />\n醒目嘅人居然少人中意"},{"pid":"539ed5fe466fe1e9d43c45c7325128ea985b17da","tid":562954,"uid":130339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T04:52:30.000Z","msg":"其實真係人夾人&hellip;<br />\n男朋友識讀心 知道人想要啲咩<br />\n醒目 唔痴身又識交代自己做緊咩 專一 拍拖重視對方之餘唔會冇咗自己<br />\n有理想 有主見 識諗 夠理性<br />\n平時唔會特別提住/講sweet嘢 但係間唔中講一講又會sweet親<br />\n亦友亦男友呢種關係好舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}